174 A.3d 521 NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. M.P., DEFENDANT-PETITIONER, IN THE MATTER OF A.P., A MINOR-RESPONDENT.

C-136 September Term 2017

079059 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000556-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
